g src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5201d352364135b9c1bfb7345fa999ecaad6974","tid":250222,"uid":36964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"99.9%沒有按足程序完成所有化驗，便批出合格證明書<br />\nICAC其實可以收case<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03aa846fdf35f21d3df74b50bd3e468eabb652a","tid":250222,"uid":25148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:27:41.000Z","msg":"又可以洗多一千億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4c52b74f941d79a94b9386e8b2efbf6257e864","tid":250222,"uid":15336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"好老實<br />\n做工程邊間都一樣<br />\n驗料驗泥乜都好<br />\n做lab永遠得兩種結果<br />\n一係就俾得錢一定唔會肥你<br />\n一係就肥左當冇做過test拎多件/搵多個位去驗 驗到得為止先交report上去<br />\n<br />\n石矢同鐵就最易pass既<br />\n石矢基本上原車黎既係冇問題係的確合格既<br />\n不過現場落果時有冇變數就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐵就仲易 永遠訂鐵都係<br />\n用十紥鐵就會訂十紥加十枝鐵<br />\n講到明果十技拎去驗<br />\n鐵廠會識做"},{"pid":"882b3f5be3ee19affa7c5d39044b0b86d9c727b9","tid":250222,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:32:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為左冧橋鋪定路，將來有事可以全部瀨晒落條友身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會有人送條 lan 線俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764fb44b3ebfda8fc93f5b603bbb32fc6d38fe92","tid":250222,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"$34.5做替死鬼"},{"pid":"c1fd2b9c4e5dc553e5ca9d5f73bcde283ac37f59","tid":250222,"uid":15336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:33:38.000Z","msg":"我之前收mill cert <br />\n外國廠既鐵<br />\n見到佢個standard竟然係跟印度<br />\n如果用返英國標準係會當肥